property.value: The Willow Creek Cottage - 18 Willow Creek Ln

property.name: flavor_text
property.value: Nestled beside a quiet creek, this charming old cottage feels peaceful during the day. But as twilight falls, a different atmosphere creeps in. Objects shift when backs are turned, and a heavy chill settles in certain rooms. See if you can uncover the source before night truly falls.
